body.name: LYNICESHOP 2-tier Over Sink Dish Dry Rack, Dish Drying Rack Cutlery Drainer Kitchen Cup Dampproof Stainless Steel Dishes Drainer with Utensil Holder for Kitchen Space Saving (25.6*11.02*32.28 Inch)
features: Sturdy and Durable: The high-quality carbon steel, baking varnish process and sturdy structure make it durable, wear-resistant, and not easy to rust. The stable triangular structure has a more even force and is less likely to tilt. The high load-bearing capacity of 22.05 lbs per tier ensures safe storage of all kinds of dishes and kitchenware.

Large Storage Space: The different racks (plate rack, bowl rack, knife rack, chopping board rack, chopstick cage, sanitaryware basket) and 8 hooks can store bowls, plates, dishes and kitchen cleaning products separately. Meanwhile, the two separate compartments provide more convenience for categorized storage, and the top shelf can also be used as a shelf for different sizes of kitchenware.

SophisticatedDesign: You can place different kitchen utensils according to the spacing of the dish net (0.79 inches) and bowl net (1.57 inches). The chopstick basket, sanitary ware basket, knife rack, chopping board rack, and hooks can all be freely moved, and you can install tools according to your own needs. The hollowed-out panel allows water to drip directly into the sink, preventing water stains from contaminating the countertop and maintaining its cleanliness.

Reasonable Size: The appropriate size(25.6*11.02*32.28-inch) allows you to avoid touching your head, blocking your hands, or obstructing your vision, making it more convenient to use. At the same time, it effectively utilizes the space above the sink, freeing up your countertop space, which is especially suitable for small kitchens/apartments.

Beautiful Appearance: The full color and classic black make it harmonious with the kitchen. The smooth surface and open construction make the product easier to clean with a rag. The detailed installation diagram, the complete installation parts and the simple structure make the installation easier.
body.description: DescriptionA multifunctional kitchen rack is the key to keeping the kitchen tidy. This 2-tier over-sink dish drying rack is made of high-quality carbon steel, which is sturdy, durable, and does not shake. Various types of storage baskets and high load-bearing capacity allow you to easily store various kitchen utensils to meet your daily needs. A reasonable and exquisite exterior design is both aesthetically pleasing and practical. With it, you will have a larger kitchen space and keep the kitchen clean.SpecificationColor: BlackStyle: ModernMartial: Carbon SteelShape: RectangularAssembly Required: YesNumber of Shelves: 2Process: Baking VarnishMounting Type: Over Sink/Kitchen CountertopLoad-bearing(Each Tier): 10kg/22.05lbProduct Inner Length: 62cm/24.41inLeg Rail Height: 9cm/3.54inTop Tray Width: 25.5cm/10.04inFirst Tier Spacing: 21cm/8.26inSecond Tier Spacing: 36cm/14.17inDish Net Spacing: 2cm/0.79inchBowl Net Spacing: 4cm/1.57inchOverall Product Size: 65*28*82cm/25.6*11.02*32.28inchPackage Size:78*19*13.5cm/30.71*7.48*5.31inchGuardrail Height: 6cm/2.36inchGross Weight: 4kg/8.82lbsNet Weight: 3.7kg/8.16lb‎sPackage Included1*2-Tier Over Sink Dish Drying Rack1*English Installation DiagramAll Accessories for AssemblyNotesPlease measure the relevant dimensions before purchasing.
